structure.unit: COUNTY AND CITY BRIDGES, TUNNELS, AND FERRIES

law.history: Repealed 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 283. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 3037k-14.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Ordinance to determine whether bridge is to be free or toll; taxation for free bridge; tolls.
